'''M41'''（又稱'''NGC 2287'''）是位於[[大犬座|大犬座]]的一個[[疏散星團|疏散星團]]，它是[[義大利|義大利]]天文學家[[Giovanni_Batista_Hodierna|Giovanni Batista Hodierna]]早在1654年以前就發現的星團，而且[[亞里斯多德|亞里斯多德]]有可能在前325年 就知道它的存在<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://messier.seds.org/more/m041_ari.html |title=M41 possibly recorded by Aristotle |accessdate=2016-01-10 |archive-date=2017-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418184854/http://messier.seds.org/more/m041_ari.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。M41幾乎就位於[[天狼星|天狼星]]的正南方，相距僅僅只有4度左右，並且[[大犬座μ2|大犬座μ<sup>2</sup>]]構成一個三角形，並且使用雙筒望遠鏡可以在視野中同時看見這三個天體。這個星團涵蓋的區域大約與滿月相當
<ref name="kambic09">{{cite book|last=Kambic|first=Bojan|title=Viewing the Constellations with Binoculars: 250+ Wonderful Sky Objects to See and Explore|publisher=Springer|location=New York, New York|date=2009|pages=230|isbn=0387853553|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3vxLNPNHOcwC&pg=PA230&dq=Sirius+%22M+41%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=RrAkU9j3Bs-okgXll4GoBg&ved=0CEMQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=Sirius%20%22M%2041%22&f=false|access-date=2016-01-10|archive-date=2015-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150102123651/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3vxLNPNHOcwC&pg=PA230&dq=Sirius+%22M+41%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=RrAkU9j3Bs-okgXll4GoBg&ved=0CEMQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=Sirius%20%22M%2041%22&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><!-- cites two previous sentences -->，包含百餘顆恆星，其中有幾顆是[[紅巨星|紅巨星]]，還有一些白矮星。最亮的一顆靠近星團的中心，視星等為6.3等，是[[光譜類型|光譜類型]]為K3的巨星<ref>Koester, D. Reimers, D. (1981), "Spectroscopic identification of white dwarfs in Galactic Clusters I. NGC2287 and NGC3532", Astronomy & Astrophysics, 99, L8-11</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=De Laet|first=Rony|title=The Casual Sky Observer's Guide: Stargazing with Binoculars and Small Telescopes|publisher=Springer|location=New York, New York|date=2011|pages=95–97|isbn=1461405955|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3fhBelJk-30C&pg=PA95&dq=Messier+41&hl=en&sa=X&ei=6q0kU4fmI4bwlAXW0oGQCg&ved=0CFEQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=Messier%2041&f=false|language=|access-date=2016-01-10|archive-date=2014-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316024822/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=3fhBelJk-30C&pg=PA95&dq=Messier+41&hl=en&sa=X&ei=6q0kU4fmI4bwlAXW0oGQCg&ved=0CFEQ6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=Messier%2041&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Dobbie, P., Day-Jones, A., Williams, K., Casewell, S., Burleigh, M., Lodieu, N., Parker, Q., Baxter, R., (2012), "Further investigation of white dwarfs in the open clusters NGC2287 and NGC3532", [[Monthly_notices_of_the_Royal_Astronomical_Society|Monthly notices of the Royal Astronomical Society]], 423, 2815-2828</ref>。估計這個團正以每秒23.3公里的速度遠離地球<ref name="simbad">{{cite web
  | title=SIMBAD Astronomical Database
  | work=Results for Messier 41
  | url=http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/Simbad
  | accessdate=2006-12-21
  | archive-date=2019-05-01
  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501023034/http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/
  | dead-url=no
  }}</ref>。這個星團的直徑在25-26[[光年|光年]]，年齡大約是1億9000萬年，但是依據星團的屬性和動態，認為這個星團的壽命大約只有5億年，而在這之前就會瓦解<ref name=Stoyan />。

[[Walter_Scott_Houston|Walter Scott Houston]]用小望遠鏡描述了這個星團的外觀<ref name="WSH">
{{cite book
 | last = Houston  | first = Walter Scott
 | date = 2005
 | title = Deep-Sky Wonders
 | pages=
 | publisher = [[Sky_Publishing_Corporation|Sky Publishing Corporation]]
 | isbn = 1-931559-23-6
}}</ref>：

<blockquote>
許多目視觀測者表示看見M41的恆星形成曲線。它們在照片中雖然不顯眼，但在我的10吋[[反射望遠鏡|反射望遠鏡]]這些曲線卻很明顯，而且靠近星團中心的亮紅色恆星非常突出。
</blockquote>

